metadata.title: Infaunal/Epifaunal

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries

metadata.description: This data base contains a biomass profile of infaunal and epifaunal organisms and includes some profiles of specific organisms such as king crab, shrimp, amphipods, and clams.
keywords: Yukon Delta NWR to Unimck Island
